, Patrick Cy", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Lau, Susanna Kp", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Yuen, Kwok-yung", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Animals", "China", "Chiroptera", "Communicable Diseases, Emerging", "Coronavirus", "Humans", "Influenza A Virus, H5N1 Subtype", "Influenza in Birds", "Influenza, Human", "Poultry", "Severe Acute Respiratory Syndrome", "Zoonoses", "Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/890af63a9645290af44c2d861a70de71", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/b5b448d9921403977cf592f691811e5f607177b358287e07d14466153ba3d023", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/HN5L68RA", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/HN5L68RA", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/9698bb8e41cc560f6388fa9c387a54e6!/b134378-136656", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "5", "pages": "401-407", "title": "Current Opinion in Infectious Diseases", "volume": "19"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/890af63a9645290af44c2d861a70de71"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:HN5L68RA"}, {"identifier": "10.1097/01.qco.0000244043.08264.fc"}], "communities": [{"id": "batlit"}, {"id": "biosyslit"}], "relations": {"version": [{"index": 0, "is_last": true, "parent": {"pid